abstract: >-
  A ready-to-fork Claude Code template for academic research — slides, papers,
  data analysis, and Monte Carlo simulation studies. Verification-gated by
  design: fan-out review fleets with hallucination gates, numeric-claim
  reproducibility audits against code, an enforcing pre-commit quality gate,
  and a validated difference-in-differences / event-study workflow built on
  the Callaway–Sant'Anna ecosystem.
